#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "⚠️ Sensitive Content Notice"
msgstr "⚠️ Isaziso somxholo onobuzaza"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"This module includes content that may be sensitive. You can check it out by yourself first. This will prepare you well for sharing the content with your teen and others afterwards.\n"
"\n"
"If you need support, see the “Support Contacts” section in your Library for help."
msgstr ""
"Esi sifundo siquka umxholo ongabanobuthathaka. Ungazikhangelela ngokunokwakho kuqala. Lonto ingakulungiselela kakuhle ukwabelana nomxholo nomntwana wakho ofikisayo kunye nabanye emva koko.\n"
"\n"
"Ukuba udinga inkxaso, jonga kwicandelo \"Uqhagamshelwano lwenkxaso\" kwithala leencwadi ukuze uncedakale."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Today's topic is about rules.\n"
"\n"
"Rules help teens understand what is expected of them – both online and offline.\n"
"\n"
"Teens are more likely to follow rules if you create the rules WITH your teen and praise them for it!"
msgstr ""
"Isihloko sanamhlanje singemithetho.\n"
"\n"
"Imithetho inceda abantwana abafikisayo baqonde ukuba yintoni elindelekileyo kubo.- zombini kwi intanethi nangaphandle kwe intanethi.\n"
"\n"
"Abantwana abafikisayo ngabona bayilandelayo imithetho ukuba uye uyenze kunye nomntwana wakho ofikisayo kwaye ubancome ngayo!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Should rules be important for you and your family? Click play to find out"
msgstr "Ingaba kufanele ibaluleke imithetho kuwe nakusapho lwakho? Cofa udlala ukufumanisa"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Greetings, everyone.\n"
"\n"
"Today's topic is rules.\n"
"\n"
"Rules promote peace within the household and promote understanding amongst family members.\n"
"\n"
"Rules promote responsibilities for each family member; therefore, it is important to have family rules.\n"
"\n"
"A household with family rules lives in peace."
msgstr ""
"Molweni, kuni nonke.\n"
"\n"
"Umxholo wanamhlanje yimithetho.\n"
"\n"
"Imithetho ikhuthaza uxolo ekhayeni ize ikhuthaze ukuqondana phakathi kwamalungu osapho.\n"
"\n"
"Imithetho ikhuthaza uxanduva kwilungu ngalinye losapho, ngoko, kubalulekile ukuba nemithetho yosapho.\n"
"\n"
"Ikhaya elinemithetho yosapho liphila ngoxolo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "When we make rules together, teens see that rules are not there to control them but to make sure everyone is safe and respected. Setting rules as a family helps build trust and responsibility for both teens and caregivers."
msgstr "Xana sisenza imithetho kunye, abantwana abafikisayo bayabona ukuba imithetho ayibekwa ukuzobalawula bona kodwa ukuqinisekisa ukuba wonke umntu wonke ukhuselekile kwaye uhloniphekile. Ukubeka imithetho njengo sapho kunceda ukwakha ukuthembana kunye noxanduva kubo bobabini umntwana ofikisayo nomkhathaleli."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.media_female_7.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Rules worked for @data.characters.media_female_7.name and her teens. Tap play to hear more"
msgstr "Imithetho imsebenzele u@data.characters.media_female_7.name kunye nabantwana bakhe abafikisayo. Cofa udlala ukuva ngakumbi"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @global.app_name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"My teenagers always just disappeared. I did not know where they were and I would get so worried and angry with them. I used to say, “This is my house, and these are my rules, if you do not want to follow them you can leave and stay in your own place.”\n"
"\n"
"When we learnt in @global.app_name about rules, I learnt that there are rules for teens and for adults and for everyone. If we follow the rules as parents, our teens will follow our example.\n"
"\n"
"I explained my worry and we all agreed: We all follow the rule and say where we are going when we leave the house. Coming up with rules together helped us a lot, as my teens do not see me anymore as that annoying parent that just makes up unnecessary rules."
msgstr ""
"Abantwana bam abafikisayo basoloko benyamalala. Ndiye ndingabazi apho bakhoyo kwaye ndiyakhathazeka kakhulu kwaye ndibanimsindo ngakubo. Bendiqhele ukuthi, Yindlu yam lena, kwaye yimithetho yam, ukuba awufuni kuyilandela ungahamba uyokuzihlalela kweyakho indawo.\n"
"\n"
"Xana besifunde ku @global.app_name malunga nemithetho, Ndifunde into yokuba kunemithetho yabantwana abafikisayo kunye neyabantu abadala kunye neyomntu wonke. Ukuba silandela imithetho singabazali, abantwana bethu abafikisayo bazakulandela umzekelo wethu.\n"
"\n"
"Ndikucacisile ukuxhalaba kwam kubo kwaye sivumelene: Sonke silandela umthetho kwaye siyatsho ukuba siyaphi xana simnka endlini. Ukuza nemithetho sisonke kuncede kakhulu, njengabantwana bam abafikisayo abandiboni njengamzali odikayo kwakhona owenza nje imithetho engenamsebenzi."

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_son_18.name
#.      @data.characters.f1_mother.name:
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Let's read what happened with @data.characters.f1_son_18.name and his mother, @data.characters.f1_mother.name:"
msgstr "Makhe sifunde ngokwenzeke ku@data.characters.f1_son_18.name kunye nomama wakhe @data.characters.f1_mother.name:"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "You always come home late!"
msgstr "Usoloko ubuya emva kwexesha!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "No I don’t, I don’t even know what late means! Stop nagging me."
msgstr "Hayi andizange, andiyazi noba ukufika emva kwexesha kuthetha ukuthini! Yeka ukundidika."

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_mother.name
#.      @data.characters.f1_son_18.name
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Making rules as a team builds trust. Let’s see how @data.characters.f1_mother.name and @data.characters.f1_son_18.name tried this the next day."
msgstr "Ukwenza imithetho njengeqembu kwakha ukuthembana. Makhe sibone u@data.characters.f1_mother.name no@data.characters.f1_son_18.name bayizame njani kusuku olulandelayo."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_son_18.name, should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I want you to have fun, @data.characters.f1_son_18.name, but I’m also worried about you staying out late. Do you know why?"
msgstr "Ndifuna wonwabe, @data.characters.f1_son_18.name, kodwa nam ndiyakhathazeka ngokubuya kwakho sekuhlwile. Uyayazi ngoba kutheni?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Because you want me to have enough time for my schoolwork?"
msgstr "Kuba ufuna ndibenexesha elaneleyo lomsebenzi wam wesikolo?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That is right. It is also not safe in this area to be outside after sunset. What do you think would be a good time for you to be home?"
msgstr "Unyanisile. Kwaye akukhuselekanga kulengingqi ukuba ngaphandle emva kokutshona kwelanga. Ucinga ukuba ingaba leliphi ixesha elilungileyo lakho lokuba sekhaya?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I could come home at 10pm?"
msgstr "Ndingabuya ekhaya ngo10?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That is a bit late, what about 6pm?"
msgstr "Sekuhlwile kancinci, unjani u6pm?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Maybe we can agree I will come home at 6pm on school nights and 10pm on Fridays and Saturdays?"
msgstr "Mhlawumbi singavumelana ngokubuyela ekhaya ngo6pm ngentsuku zesikolo kwaye ngo10pm ngoLwezihlanu nangeMigqibelo?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes, great. From now on, our household rule is that you need to come home at 6pm on school nights and 10pm on Fridays and Saturdays. But you always walk home with a friend. Okay?"
msgstr "Ewe, kuhle. Sukela ngoku ukuya phambili, umthetho wethu wasekhaya uthi kufuneka ubuye ngo 6pm ngentsuku zesikolo uphinde ngo10pm ngoLwezihlanu nangeMigqibelo. Kodwa rhoqo uhambe nomhlobo ukubuyela ekhaya. Kulungile?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Okay, mother."
msgstr "Kulungile, mama."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_son_18.name, should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Thank you very much, @data.characters.f1_son_18.name, for helping to come up with a good rule together. I am proud to see how responsible you are getting."
msgstr "Enkosi kakhulu, @data.characters.f1_son_18.name, ngokundincedisa senze umthetho olungileyo kunye. Ndiyazidla ukubona indlela oya ubanexanduva ngayo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "*The next day...*"
msgstr "*Usuku olulandelayo...*"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_son_18.name, should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Thank you, @data.characters.f1_son_18.name, for coming home on time. After you finish your schoolwork, we can have your favourite meal for dinner."
msgstr "Enkosi, @data.characters.f1_son_18.name, ngokubuya ekhaya kwangethuba. Emva kokugqiba umsebenzi wakho wesikolo, singafumana isidlo osithandayo sangokuhlwa."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Let's think about what happened in this story."
msgstr "Makhe sicinge malunga nokwenzekileyo kweli bali."

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_son_18.name
#.      @data.characters.f1_mother.name,
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "What went well when @data.characters.f1_son_18.name and his mother, @data.characters.f1_mother.name, made a rule together?"
msgstr "Yintoni ehambe kakuhle @data.characters.f1_son_18.name kunye nomama wakhe, @data.characters.f1_mother.name, benze umthetho kunye?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "They discussed the reasons behind the rule"
msgstr "Baye bancokola ngezizathu zomthetho"

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_mother.name
#.      @data.characters.f1_son_18.name's
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "@data.characters.f1_mother.name listened to @data.characters.f1_son_18.name's suggestions"
msgstr "@data.characters.f1_mother.name umamele amacebiso ka@data.characters.f1_son_18.name"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "The rule was clear, specific and fair"
msgstr "Umthetho ubucacile, ungqalile yaye ulungile"

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_mother.name
#.      @data.characters.f1_son_18.name
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "@data.characters.f1_mother.name praised @data.characters.f1_son_18.name for helping to make the rule"
msgstr "@data.characters.f1_mother.name umncomile u@data.characters.f1_son_18.name ngokumnceda enze umthetho"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That is right, making clear rules together in a calm and positive way works so well!"
msgstr "Kulungile, ukwenza imithetho ecacileyo kunye ngendlela ezolileyo nangendlela elungileyo kusebenze kakuhle kakhulu!"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_son_18.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "How do you think @data.characters.f1_son_18.name knew his mother appreciated him?"
msgstr "Ucinga ukuba u@data.characters.f1_son_18.name wazi njani ukuba umama wakhe uye wambulela?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "She praised him"
msgstr "Uye wamncoma"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "She rewarded him when he followed the rule"
msgstr "Umnike umvuzo ngokulandela umthetho"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Exactly - a positive response makes all the difference!"
msgstr "Uchanile - impendulo eyiyo iyawenza umahluko!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Here are this week’s takeaway skills to help learn how to set rules with your teen!"
msgstr "Nazi izakhono onokuzithatha kuleveki ukukunceda ufunde ukuba ungayibeka njani imithetho kunye nomntwana wakho ofikisayo!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "TEAM RULES"
msgstr "IMITHETHO YEQELA"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Household rules help to keep our teenagers safe and to understand what is expected from them. When you involve a teenager in making rules they are more likely to follow them."
msgstr "Imithetho yekhaya inceda ukugcina abantwana bethu abafikisayo bekhuselekile kwaye baqonde ukuba yintoni elindelekileyo kubo. Xa umbandakanya umntwana wakho ofikisayo ekwenzeni imithetho banokuzimisela ngakumbi ekuyilandeleni."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "REAL RULES"
msgstr "IMITHETHO YOKWENENE"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Plan rules WITH your teenager. Start with one new rule first – you can add another one later. Discuss the reasons for the rule and listen to their views."
msgstr "Cwangcisa KUNYE nomntwana wakho ofikisayo imithetho. Qala ngomthetho omnye omtsha - ungongezelela omnye mva. Xoxani ngezizathu zalemithetho kwaye umamele izimvo zabo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "More tips"
msgstr "Ezinye iingcebiso"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Talk with your teen about why rules are important both online and offline."
msgstr "Thetha nomntwana wakho ofikisayo ngokuba kutheni imithetho ibalulekile kuzo zombini i-intanethi nangaphandle kwe intanethi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "PRAISE RULES!"
msgstr "IMITHETHO YOKUNCOMA!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Praise your teen for planning a rule with you, and praise them for keeping it! Positive feedback helps teens make good choices, including in relationships and online."
msgstr "Ncoma umntwana wakho ofikisayo ngokucwangcisa imithetho kunye nawe, mcome ngokuyigcina! Ingxelo eyakhayo inceda abantwana abafikisayo ukuba benze ukhetho olulungileyo, kubandakanya ubudlelwane kunye ne intanethi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Rules are important to keep your teens safe – not only offline, but also online. There’s more about this in the lesson on teen safety, but let’s already have a first look now!"
msgstr "Imithetho ibalulekile ukugcina umntwana wakho ofikisayo ekhuselekile - hayi kuphela ngaphandle kwe intanethi, kodwa nakwi-intanethi. Kukho okungakumbi ngalento kwisifundo malunga nokhuseleko lomntwana wakho ofikisayo, kodwa masiqalise sijonge ngoku!"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_daughter_13.name, should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "@data.characters.f1_daughter_13.name, have you done your homework?"
msgstr "@data.characters.f1_daughter_13.name, uwenzile umsebenzi wakho wasekhaya?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Just a minute mother, I’m finishing this Tiktok video."
msgstr "Umzuzu nje mama, Ndisagqibezela i vidiyo ka Tiktok."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "You are a really great dancer! Tell me about why you like TikTok."
msgstr "Ungumdanisi obalaseleyo ngokwenene! Ndixelele isizathu sokuba uthande uTiktok."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "All my friends are on it, mother. I have more than 600 likes and 120 followers."
msgstr "Bonke abahlobo bam bakuye, mama. Ndinenani elingapha ko 600 labathandi kunye no 120 yabalandeli."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_daughter_13.name. should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"I’m proud of how well you dance, @data.characters.f1_daughter_13.name. But we need to make sure you are safe.\n"
"\n"
"I know your friends look at TikTok, but with an open account, there are other people who look at videos of teenagers for their own sexual needs. Sometimes they contact teenagers. They pretend to be nice but end up threatening and abusing teens."
msgstr ""
"Ndiyazingca ngendlela entle odanisa ngayo, @data.characters.f1_daughter_13.name. Kodwa kufuneka siqiniseke ukuba ukhuselekile.\n"
"\n"
"Ndiyayazi abahlobo bakho bayamjonga uTikTok, kodwa nge akhawunti evuliweyo, kukho abantu abajonga imiboniso yabantwana abafikisayo ngeezidingo zesondo zabo. Ngamanye amaxesha baqhagamshelana nabantwana abafikisayo. Bazenza ngathi balungile kodwa ekugqibeleni baphela beboyikisa kwaye bebahlukumeza."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Let’s look together online at how we can keep this fun for you but also safe. \n"
"\n"
"Look – you can make your account private and control who follows you. So you can accept people you know from school and our community, but not people you don't know who contact you online.\n"
"\n"
"Can we make a rule together that you can use TikTok, but with a private account? I trust you to know who to accept!"
msgstr ""
"Masijonge kunye kumakhasi onxibelelwano ukuba singayigcina njani isonwabisa kuwe kodwa ibe ikhuselekile. \n"
"\n"
"Jonga – ungenza i akhawunti yakho ibeyi mfihlo kwaye ulawule abakulandelayo. Ngoko ke ungakwazi ukwamkela abantu obaziyo esikolweni kunye nasekuhlaleni, kodwa hayi abantu ongabaziyo abaxhulumana nawe.\n"
"\n"
"Singakwazi ukwenza umthetho kunye ongakwazi ukuwusebenzisa kuTikTok, kodwa nge akhawunti eyimfihlo? Ndikuthembile ukuba uyabazi ozakubamkela!"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_daughter_13.name! should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I’m proud of you, @data.characters.f1_daughter_13.name!"
msgstr "Ndiyazingca ngawe, @data.characters.f1_daughter_13.name!"

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_daughter_13.name
#.      @data.characters.f1_mother.name
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"It was wonderful to see @data.characters.f1_daughter_13.name and @data.characters.f1_mother.name make a rule together. \n"
"\n"
"Now let's practice making rules.\n"
"\n"
"Write down one important rule you would like to make with your teenager – you will be doing this as your home practice this week."
msgstr ""
"Bekukuhle ukubona u @data.characters.f1_daughter_13.name no @data.characters.f1_mother.name besenza umthetho kunye. \n"
"\n"
"Ngoku makhe sizame ukwenza imithetho.\n"
"\n"
"Bhala phantsi umthetho omnye obalulekileyo ongathanda ukuwenza kunye nomntwana wakho ofikisayo - uzokuba usenza lento njengomsebenzi wasekhaya kule veki."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"**Here are some examples of rules other families made:**\n"
"- ⚽ Teen can play outside after finishing homework\n"
"- 👪🏽 All family members eat dinner together\n"
"- 💬 We talk about anything that worries us – no keeping secrets.\n"
"- 📱 We use phones responsibly – no phones at bedtime and only private accounts.\n"
"- ❤️ We treat others with respect, online and offline."
msgstr ""
"**Nantsi eminye imizekelo yemigaqo eyenziwa zezinye iintsapho.**\n"
"- ⚽ Abantwana abafikisayo bangadlala phandle xa begqibile ukwenza umsebenzi wasekhaya\n"
"- 👪🏽 Onke amalungu osapho atya isidlo sangokuhlwa kunye\n"
"- 💬 Sithetha ngento yonke esixhalabisayo - akugcinwa ziyimfihlo. \n"
"- 📱 Sisebenzisa ifowuni ngenkathalo - akuvumelekanga fowuni ngexesha lokulala, kuphela i akhawunti zabucala.\n"
"- ❤️ Siphatha abanye ngentlonipho, kwi intanethi nangaphandle kwe intanethi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"This week's home activity is to set one rule together with your teen.\n"
"\n"
"Remember to praise your teen afterwards!"
msgstr ""
"Owaleveki umsebenzi, kukwenza umthetho ube mnye nomntwana wakho ofikisayo.\n"
"\n"
"Khumbula ukumncoma umntwana wakho ofikisayo emva koko!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"**Remember to use your skills for rule setting:**\n"
"\n"
"⚽ Team rules: When making the rule, work together like a team. \n"
"🔎 Real rules: Agree on real rules that are clear and fair. For example, you could agree that everyone says where they are going before leaving the house.\n"
"🎉 Praise rules: Praise when rules are followed!"
msgstr ""
"**Khumbula ukusebenzisa izakhono zokuseka imithetho:**\n"
"\n"
"⚽ Imithetho yeqela: Xa nisenza umthetho, sebenzani njengeqela.\n"
"🔎 Imithetho eyiyo: Vumelanani kwimithetho eyiyo ecacileyo kwaye elungileyo. Umzekelo, ningavumelana ekubeni wonke umntu atsho ukuba uyaphi phambi kokuba ahambe endlini.\n"
"🎉 Imithetho yokuncoma: Ncoma xa imithetho ilandelwe!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Can you set one rule together with your teen this week?"
msgstr "Ungakwazi ukumisela umthetho ubemnye kunye nomntwana wakho ofikisayo kuleveki?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "Ewe"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Fantastic! Setting a rule together helps your teen feel involved and respected. It is a big step toward building trust and cooperation."
msgstr "Kwakuhle! Ukumisela umthetho kunye kumnceda umntwana wakho ofikisayo azive ebandakanyekile kwaye ehloniphekile. Lelona nyathelo elikhulu ekwakheni ukuthembana nokusebenzisana."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I think so"
msgstr "Ndicinga njalo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "You can do it! Even beginning the conversation shows your teen that their voice matters. Take it one step at a time."
msgstr "Ungayenza! Kwaye nokuqala incoko ibonisa umntwana wakho ofikisayo ukuba ilizwi lakhe libalulekile. Thatha inyathelo libelinye ngexesha."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "No"
msgstr "Hayi"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That's okay. It can take time to agree on new rules. You could start by asking your teen what they think is important - small talks can lead to big changes."
msgstr "Kulungile. Ingathatha ixesha ukuvumelana ngemithetho emitsha. Ungaqala ngokubuza umntwana wakho ofikisayo ukuba ucinga yintoni ebalulekileyo - intetho ezincinci zingakhokhelela kutshintsho olukhulu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Clear, simple rules made together with your teen are not about control - they are about keeping them safe and building responsibility. When teens understand the reasons behind the rules, they are more likely to follow them."
msgstr "Imithetho ecacileyo nelula eniyenze kunye nomntwana wakho ofikisayo ayikho ngokulawula - ingokubagcina bekhuselekile kunye nokwakha uxanduva. Xa abantwana abafikisayo beziqonda izizathu ezingaphaya kwemithetho, bangakwazi ukuyilandela kakuhle."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.media_daughter_2.name's should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Can teens value rules too? Hear @data.characters.media_daughter_2.name's story"
msgstr "Ingaba abantwana abafikisayo bangayixabisa imithetho nabo? Mamela ibali lika @data.characters.media_daughter_2.name"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"I never liked rules and I used to forget rules a lot.\n"
"\n"
"One day, I was playing with my friends. The rule at home was that we should be in the yard by 6pm, but I forgot again. By 6:30 it was getting dark and I was still outside and playing with my phone. Then a boy came, grabbed my phone and ran away.\n"
"\n"
"I understood that rules can really help to keep us safe, so I changed my behaviour and I was in the yard by 5pm from then."
msgstr ""
"Andizange ndiyithande imithetho kwaye bendisoloko ndiyilibala kakhulu.\n"
"\n"
"Ngenye imini, Bendidlala kunye nabahlobo bam. Umthetho ekhaya yayikukuba kufuneka sibesengaphakathi ngo 6pm, kodwa ndalibala kwakhona. Nge 6:30 bekusele kumnyama kwaye bendisengaphandle kwaye ndidlala nge fowuni yam. Ngoko umfana weza, waxutha ifowuni yam waye wabaleka.\n"
"\n"
"Ndayiqonda ukuba imithetho ingalunceda ngokwenene ukusigcina sikhuselekile, ngoko ndatshintsha isimilo sam kwaye ndabangaphakathi ngentsimbi yesi 5pm ukusukela ngoko."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Well done for taking time for yourself today. 🎉"
msgstr "Wenze kakuhle ngokuthatha ixesha lesiqu sakho namhlanje. 🎉"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Here is a short video to help you slow down before you go"
msgstr "Nali ushicilelo olufutshane elizokunceda wehlise ngaphambi kokuba uhambe"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"When everything feels like it is falling apart And you can't help but raise your voice When all the frustrations are beginning to start Remember that you have a choice\n"
"\n"
"Let's slow down Take a few deep breaths Remember all we have to be grateful for Let's slow down Take a few deep breaths Because I really couldn't love you more\n"
"\n"
"You can take pause, you can count to 10 Play a game or do something fun You can phone a friend, someone to confide in Remember you're not the only one\n"
"\n"
"Let's slow down Take a few deep breaths Remember all we have to be grateful for Let's slow down Take a few deep breaths Because I really couldn't love you more\n"
"\n"
"Let's slow down Take a few deep breaths Remember all we have to be grateful for Let's slow down Take a few deep breaths Because I really couldn't love you more Because I really couldn't love you more"
msgstr ""
"Xa yonke into ivakala ingathi iyamoshakala Kwaye awukwazi ukuzinceda uvele unyuse ilizwi Xa zonke iinzingo ziqala Khumbula ukuba ungenza ngakumbi\n"
"\n"
"Makhe sime kancinci Tsala umoya kancinci Khumbula konke esino kubulela ngako Makhe sehlise kancinci Tsala umoya kancinci Kuba andinakuthanda ngakumbi\n"
"\n"
"Yima, ungabala uyokutsho ku 10 Dlala umdlalo okanye wenze into emnandi Ungafowunela umhlobo, umntu onokumchazela ingxaki Khumbula ayinguwe wedwa\n"
"\n"
"Makhe sime kancinci Tsala umoya kancinci Khumbula konke esino kubulela ngako Makhe sime Tsala umoya kancinci Kuba bendingenokuthanda ngakumbi \n"
"\n"
"Makhe sime kancinci Tsalaa umoya Khumbula konke esino kubulela ngako Makhe sime Tsalaa umoya kancinci Kuba bendingenokuthanda ngakumbi Kuba bendingenokuthanda ngakumbi"

